name: Dark all.uddataplus.dk
css:
@-moz-document domain("all.uddataplus.dk") {
body,
.controls p,
#instnr,
#instnr::placeholder,
.input-xlarge,
.input-xlarge::placeholder,
.user-info,
.dark-blue.open,
.menu-text,
.hoverable .knappen,
.knappen,
.knappen:hover h4,
.knappen:hover p,
.control-group select,
.control-group textarea,
.control-group input[type="text"],
.control-group input[type="password"],
.control-group input[type="datetime"],
.control-group input[type="datetime-local"],
.control-group input[type="date"],
.control-group input[type="month"],
.control-group input[type="time"],
.control-group input[type="week"],
.control-group input[type="number"],
.control-group input[type="email"],
.control-group input[type="url"],
.control-group input[type="search"],
.control-group input[type="tel"],
.control-group input[type="color"],
textarea,
input[type="text"],
input[type="password"],
input[type="datetime"],
input[type="datetime-local"],
input[type="date"],
input[type="month"],
input[type="time"],
input[type="week"],
input[type="number"],
input[type="email"],
input[type="url"],
input[type="search"],
input[type="tel"],
input[type="color"],
.img-polaroid,
body,
select {
	color: white !important;
}

.page-content {
	background: none !important;
}

#wrapper,
.page-content,
body::before,
.OEGVLWD-d-e,
.modal-footer,
.CWI5AT-q-d > label:first-child {
	background-color: #333 !important;
}

.demoimg,
.mobildemoimg {
	box-shadow: none !important;
	opacity: 0.6;
	transition: all .2s;
}

.demoimg:hover,
.mobildemoimg:hover {
	opacity: 1;
}

.page-header h1,
.page-header h1 small,
.widget-header.widget-header-flat h4 {
	color: #a8c9e1;
}

a {
	color: #99cfea !important;
}

a:hover {
	text-decoration: underline;
}

.span3 div,
.dropdown-yellow li a:hover,
.nav-list > li > a:hover,
.hoverable .knappen:hover,
.knappen:hover,
.nav-tabs > li.active > a,
.nav-tabs > li.active > a:hover,
.nav-tabs > li.active > a:focus,
.nav-tabs > li > a:focus,
.OEGVLWD-c-r.OEGVLWD-c-G.OEGVLWD-c-O.OEGVLWD-c-k.OEGVLWD-c-f.OEGVLWD-q-f[style="background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); flex: 0 1 auto;"],
.table-striped tbody > tr:nth-child(2n+1) > td {
	background-color: #555 !important;
}

.OEGVLWD-c-r.OEGVLWD-c-G.OEGVLWD-c-O.OEGVLWD-c-k.OEGVLWD-c-f.OEGVLWD-q-f[style="background-color: rgb(229, 255, 225); flex: 0 1 auto;"] {
	background-color: #517f4a !important;
}

.OEGVLWD-c-r.OEGVLWD-c-G.OEGVLWD-c-O.OEGVLWD-c-k.OEGVLWD-c-f.OEGVLWD-q-f[style="background-color: rgb(255, 243, 211); font-style: italic; flex: 0 1 auto;"] {
	background-color: #7f6f43 !important;
}

#instnr,
.input-xlarge,
.ANSEYM-eb-a,
.fc-widget-header,
.ANSEYM-e-k,
.ANSEYM-e-l table,
table,
.ANSEYM-a-e,
.ANSEYM-i-r.ANSEYM-i-G.ANSEYM-i-O.ANSEYM-i-k.ANSEYM-i-f.well.well-small.ANSEYM-W-a,
.dropdown-menu,
#sidebar::before,
#sidebar,
#sidebar-collapse::before,
#sidebar-collapse,
#language,
.nav-list > li > a,
.hoverable .knappen,
.knappen,
.nav-tabs > li > a,
.profile-picture,
.control-group select,
.control-group textarea,
.control-group input[type="text"],
.control-group input[type="password"],
.control-group input[type="datetime"],
.control-group input[type="datetime-local"],
.control-group input[type="date"],
.control-group input[type="month"],
.control-group input[type="time"],
.control-group input[type="week"],
.control-group input[type="number"],
.control-group input[type="email"],
.control-group input[type="url"],
.control-group input[type="search"],
.control-group input[type="tel"],
.control-group input[type="color"],
.widget-header-flat,
.widget-body,
.collapse,
.input-append .add-on,
.input-prepend .add-on,
.select2-container.select2-container-disabled .select2-choice,
.select2-container.select2-container-disabled .select2-choice .select2-arrow,
textarea,
input[type="text"],
input[type="password"],
input[type="datetime"],
input[type="datetime-local"],
input[type="date"],
input[type="month"],
input[type="time"],
input[type="week"],
input[type="number"],
input[type="email"],
input[type="url"],
input[type="search"],
input[type="tel"],
input[type="color"],
.img-polaroid,
body,
select,
.IEA3S2-o-d,
.I00A3XB-a-C,
.sidebar-collapse > [class*="icon-"] {
	background-color: black !important;
}

img[alt=ElevPlan] {
	filter: invert(100);
}
}
